passives.effects:
Rengar collects 1 trophy when scoring a takedown against enemy champions.
 3 Trophies: Rengar gains 25 bonus movement speed while out of combat or in brush.
 6 Trophies: Unseen Predator gains 125 bonus range.
 12 Trophies: Thrill of the Hunt's duration is increased by 5 seconds.
 20 Trophies: Thrill of the Hunt's bonus movement speed while stealthed is doubled.
